Ripped at 192vbr. Since this is not music the quality was scaled back. Dammit I forgot the most important thing which is to set "REMEMBER POSITION" in the MP3 tags. That will allow you to continue where you left off when re-starting a track. The default for music is to play the song from the beginning but that doesn't work well with audio books so please do yourself a favor and set "Remember Position" in the MP3 properties.
